<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/27(Thu.) Bill and Melinda Gates are ending their marriage/ Taiwan’s total of COVID cases near 1500(host:Larry)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=501&amp;p=523#p523"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">There is no on-site meeting on 5/27<br /><br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pwd=bkR5TEwwZDlpZnBmR0ZzQ2NKSU5MQT09">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw ... NKSU5MQT09</a><!-- m --><br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks <br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation <br />8:00-8:40 pm Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation<br /></span><br />Session 1  <br />Bill and Melinda Gates are ending their marriage  <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/03/tech/bill-and-melinda-gates-divorce/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2021/05/03/tech ... index.html</a><!-- m --> <br />Question  <br />1. What is the real purpose of marriage? What is your opinion about marriage?  <br />  2. Does marriage need to give up oneself, shouldn’t have privacy or personal desires? If not, what should be done?  <br />  3. The divorce rate in Taiwan has always been quite high. Among them, the proportion of divorces only after middle age is increasing. Do you know why?  <br />4. What do you think are the main conditions for maintaining a good marriage relationship? Money, education, family background, personality, living  habits or values, etc. Which do you think are more important? why?  <br />5. What is the idea marriage in your mind? Do you think it is possible and how do you achieve it?  <br />  <br />Session 2  <br />Taiwan’s total of COVID cases near 1500  <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4203958">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4203958</a><!-- m -->  <br />1. When COVID-19 broke out in other countries and even closed the city, Taiwan may not be really understanded their fear in relatively safe Taiwan.  Now it is Taiwan turn, if Taiwan also implements the lockdown, how would you feel? <br />2. If our government order a two-week lockdown to prevent the epidemic in 24 hours, what measures will you take? Do you buy food or other items in bulk?  <br />3. A month ago, you might not want to be vaccinated. If vaccinations were the best preventive measures and available, would you reconsider receiving vaccinations? Why?  <br />4. So far, Taiwan has entered the third level of epidemic prevention measures.  Has this measure caused any inconvenience and impact on you?  <br />5. There is a shortage of nurses in Taipei. If you are a retired nurse, are you willing to contribute yourself? Why?<br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Sat May 22, 2021 5:38 pm</p><hr />
